          <h3>Haftung für Links</h3>
          <p>
            Unsere Website enthält Links zu externen Websites Dritter. Auf deren Inhalte haben wir keinen Einfluss und können daher keine Gewähr übernehmen.
          </p>

          <h3>Urheberrecht</h3>
          <p>
            Die Inhalte auf diesen Seiten unterliegen dem deutschen Urheberrecht. Die Vervielfältigung oder jede Art der Verwertung außerhalb der Grenzen des Urheberrechtes bedürfen der schriftlichen Zustimmung.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="design-credit-box">
          <h2 class="credit-title">DESIGN & ENTWICKLUNG</h2>
          <p class="credit-text">
            DIESE WEBSITE WURDE VON 
            <a href="https://r3webdesign.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="r3-link">
              <span class="r3-tag">R3</span>WEBDESIGN
            </a> 
            ENTWICKELT.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    background: #050505;
    min-height: 100vh;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .legal-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  /* --- ZURÜCK BUTTON --- */
  .back-navigation {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .back-to-stage {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: #111;
    padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
    border: 1px solid #222;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    transition: all 0.2s steps(3);
    clip-path: polygon(10% 0, 100% 0, 90% 100%, 0% 100%);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .back-to-stage:hover {
    background: #cc0000;
    transform: translateX(-5px);
    border-color: #fff;
  }

  /* --- BRAND HEADER --- */
  .brand-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .band-name {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    transform: rotate(-3deg);
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
  }

  .red-block {
    position: absolute;
    top: -25%; left: -10%;
    color: #cc0000;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 5rem);
    z-index: 5;
  }

  .white-rock-style {
    display: block;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 15vw, 9rem);
    text-shadow: 4px 4px 0px #cc0000;
    letter-spacing: -2px;
    line-height: 0.8;
  }

  /* --- CONTENT STYLING --- */
  .rock-subheading {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-top: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #cc0000;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .legal-text, .legal-block p {
    color: #888;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .legal-content h3 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: #cc0000;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* --- CONTACT BOXES --- */
  .contact-box {
    background: #111;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-left: 4px solid #cc0000;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #222;
  }

  .contact-box p {
    color: #eee;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .box-title {
    margin-top: 0 !important;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #fff !important;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
  }

  /* --- DESIGN CREDIT BOX --- */
  .design-credit-box {
    margin-top: 6rem;
    background: #111;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid #222;
    border-top: 4px solid #cc0000; 
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .credit-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .credit-text {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #888;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .r3-link {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #fff;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .r3-tag {
    background: #cc0000;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0 6px;
    font-weight: 900;
    transform: skewX(-10deg); 
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .r3-link:hover { color: #cc0000; }
  .r3-link:hover .r3-tag { background: #fff; color: #cc0000; }

  .noise {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/asfalt-dark.png');
    opacity: 0.2;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .white-rock-style { font-size: 4.5rem; }
    .red-block { font-size: 2.5rem; }
    .rock-subheading { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    .design-credit-box { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>